data.title: Lee Hyeri
data.meta_description: Lee Hyeri was a member of AKB48's Team A. Was born in Gwangju, South Korea. Has a younger sister, Hye-rim (2 years younger). Education: Seoul School of Performing Arts, Konkuk University (Film major) Acted in the dramas: “Tasty Life” (2012), “Seonam Girls High School Investigators ” (2014...
